name: dEYEversity (2011)
description: The opposing yet complementary forces: masculine vs feminine, left vs right, black vs white, yin vs yang, are both composed of the same ingredients, in this case, eyes, that are windows to the soul. Featured at the UNESCO (Paris), Moulin Rouge (Paris), Salon des Invalides (Paris), Composants (Paris), Awarded 2nd position award by the International Society of Computational Biology (ISCB) 2018.
